title: State of Decay Update 3 nosTeam, Walmart
description:
This is Patch(update) 3 for State of Decay game, its for nosTeam version of full game. However, it is also working for WALMART version of full game. Old saves working. 
Required Update 1 by Walmart OR Patch 1 by nosTEAM and patch 2 nosTEAM.

If you are using nosTEAM version:

1. Install into main directory of the game.

2. Enjoy game :)


If you are using WALMART version:


1. Install SOD_patch#3_nosTEAM.exe into main folder of the game.

2. Copy steam_api.dll from WALMART mounted image crack folder into your SOD game folder, overwrite.

3. Run game as administrator.

4. Enjoy game :)


Big Thanks and all credits to nosTEAM.
